    @Component
public class FileTargetProcessorSubmitIssues
extends AbstractProcessorBuildObjectMapsFromGroupedObjects
implements ITargetProcessorSubmitIssues
    This IProcessor implementation allows for writing data from the current Context instance to a file based on a list of configured TemplateExpression instances.
